OL,3,CHarry Maguire 'shocked and gutted' to
OL,4,Cbe left out of 2026 World Cup squad
OL,6,FEngland defender Harry Maguire says he
OL,7,Fis "shocked and gutted" to have been
OL,8,Fleft out of Thomas Tuchel's 2026 World
OL,9,FCup squad.
OL,11,FThe German coach will name his 26-man
OL,12,Fsquad for this summer's shot at glory
OL,13,Fin North America on Friday morning,
OL,14,Fand he began making calls to players
OL,15,Fthe previous day.
OL,26,@oD@DOUoD@WO]
