OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779408177
OL,3,CHarry Maguire 'shocked and gutted' to
OL,4,Cbe left out of 2026 World Cup squad
OL,6,FMaguire, 33, was part of the England
OL,7,Fsquad in March, having received his
OL,8,Ffirst call-up under Tuchel, but the 66-
OL,9,Fcap defender confirmed on social media
OL,10,Fon Thursday that he will not be going
OL,11,Fto the World Cup.
OL,13,F"I was confident I could of (sic)
OL,14,Fplayed a major part this summer for my
OL,15,Fcountry after the season I've had.
OL,16,FI've been left shocked and gutted by
OL,17,Fthe decision," the Manchester United
OL,18,Fdefender posted on Instagram.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
