OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779408177
OL,3,CHarry Maguire 'shocked and gutted' to
OL,4,Cbe left out of 2026 World Cup squad
OL,6,F"I've loved nothing more than putting
OL,7,Fthat shirt on and representing my
OL,8,Fcountry over the years. I wish the
OL,9,Fplayers all the best this summer."
OL,11,FMaguire went to the 2018 and 2022
OL,12,FWorld Cups and played a starring role
OL,13,Fin England's run to the Euro 2020
OL,14,Ffinal.
OL,16,FThe centre-back failed to make the cut
OL,17,Ffor Euro 2024 following a calf injury
OL,18,Fand, after 18 months in the
OL,19,Finternational wilderness, played in
OL,20,Fboth March friendlies under Tuchel.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
