OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779408177
OL,3,CHarry Maguire 'shocked and gutted' to
OL,4,Cbe left out of 2026 World Cup squad
OL,6,FIt is understood that Maguire's United
OL,7,Fteammate Luke Shaw has also been
OL,8,Foverlooked by Tuchel.
OL,10,FThe 30-year-old has started every
OL,11,FPremier League game this season but
OL,12,Fhas yet to get a look-in under the
OL,13,FEngland boss.
OL,15,FOther eye-catching calls could come to
OL,16,Flight before the squad is announced at
OL,17,Faround 10am on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
