OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779408177
OL,3,CHarry Maguire 'shocked and gutted' to
OL,4,Cbe left out of 2026 World Cup squad
OL,6,FThere are some headaches to consider,
OL,7,Flike how to juggle England's swathe of
OL,8,Fnumber 10 options ` with Phil Foden
OL,9,Fand Cole Palmer sweating on their
OL,10,Fspots after unimpressive seasons.
OL,12,FJude Bellingham's relationship with
OL,13,FTuchel has been under the microscope,
OL,14,Fbut he is sure to be on the plane
OL,15,Falong with Morgan Rogers, with
OL,16,FEberechi Eze and Morgan Gibbs-White
OL,17,Falso vying for a place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
