OL,3,CHarry Maguire 'shocked and gutted' to
OL,4,Cbe left out of 2026 World Cup squad
OL,6,FTrent Alexander-Arnold has been a high-
OL,7,Fprofile absentee this season but could
OL,8,Fbenefit from Ben White's injury,
OL,9,Falthough Tuchel admitted in November
OL,10,Fthat the Real Madrid right-back was
OL,11,Fbehind Jarell Quansah.
OL,13,FThe England boss needs reassuring over
OL,14,Fthe fitness of Tino Livramento, who
OL,15,Fhas been out for a month with a thigh
OL,16,Finjury, and is checking on Levi
OL,17,FColwill following the defender's
OL,18,Fpromising return to action.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
