OL,3,CHarry Maguire 'shocked and gutted' to
OL,4,Cbe left out of 2026 World Cup squad
OL,6,FNamed in Tuchel's first two squads,
OL,7,Fthe Chelsea centre-back underwent
OL,8,Fsurgery on an anterior cruciate
OL,9,Fligament injury in August and has made
OL,10,Fthree appearances since returning this
OL,11,Fmonth.
OL,13,FKey defender John Stones' lack of game
OL,14,Ftime at Manchester City is a
OL,15,Fconsideration, but the England boss
OL,16,Fsaid in March that he had "a lot of
OL,17,Fcredit in the bank".
