OL,3,CHarry Maguire 'shocked and gutted' to
OL,4,Cbe left out of 2026 World Cup squad
OL,6,FDan Burn looks set to be included,
OL,7,Falong with Marc Guehi and Ezri Konsa,
OL,8,Fafter Maguire's omission. Trevoh
OL,9,FChalobah is another fighting for his
OL,10,Fspot. Ollie Watkins will surely be
OL,11,Frecalled, having been dropped in March.
OL,13,FDominic Calvert-Lewin and Dominic
OL,14,FSolanke were trialled as captain Harry
OL,15,FKane's back-up, but neither shone, and
OL,16,Fthe Aston Villa striker has scored 10
OL,17,Fsince being overlooked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
