OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FDanny Welbeck, 35, is admired by the
OL,12,Fcoaching staff but has not played for
OL,13,FEngland since 2018.
OL,15,FKobbie Mainoo's resurgence at United
OL,16,Fputs him in with a strong shout, while
OL,17,FAdam Wharton and James Garner ` man of
OL,18,Fthe match on his March debut against
OL,19,FUruguay ` are pushing for inclusion.
