OL,3,CHarry Maguire 'shocked and gutted' to
OL,4,Cbe left out of 2026 World Cup squad
OL,6,FThe Football Association has to submit
OL,7,Fa 26-man squad to FIFA on May 31, but
OL,8,Fcan make changes to outfield players
OL,9,Ffor medical reasons up until 24 hours
OL,10,Fbefore the Group L opener against
OL,11,FCroatia on June 17.
OL,13,FOnly goalkeepers can be changed after
OL,14,Fthis point. Brighton's Jason Steele is
OL,15,Fset to travel as a training goalkeeper
OL,16,F` a role filled by Tom Heaton at Euro
OL,17,F2024.
